Mounting Procedure
==================


You can mount |productP| with VESA mounting (:ref:`guide <vesa_mguide>`): |vesa_screws| screws.

You can mount |productP| with panel mounting method (:ref:`guide <panel_mguide>`).

You can also mount |productP| with wall mounting or desktop mounting method.

.. attention::

    Please make sure the display is not exposed to high pressure when mounting into an enclosure.

You can find detailed information about mounting in the |mguide|.